headline: Fair Isaac's Fair Value Slips By 15%
summary: Fair Isaac faces new regulatory challenges as VantageScore gains acceptance, eroding its monopoly in credit scoring for U.S. mortgages. Read why FICO is a Sell.

headline: Fair Isaac's Growth And Moat Under Fire With New Challenges
summary: Fair Isaac (FICO) is rated 'Hold' after a 38% drop from its 52-week high, driven by regulatory changes allowing VantageScore competition.

headline: BigBear.ai (BBAI) Moves 12.9% Higher: Will This Strength Last?
summary: BigBear.ai (BBAI) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
